361 void LineValidationTableCreation::ExamineValidationTable(int SEARCH_LINE_CODE, vector<LineValidationTable>&table)

368

370  else{table[i].SetAdjacentPointPredictionFound(SEARCH_LINE_CODE,true);}
371 
372  if(AdjacentValidationTableIsEmpty(SEARCH_LINE_CODE)){continue;}
373 
374  Point min_distance_adjacent_point;
375  int min_distance_adjacent_point_id;

379 
380  if(min_distance < kMaxPointDistance_)
381  {
382  table[i].SetAdjacentPointPrediction(SEARCH_LINE_CODE,true);
383  table[i].SetAdjacentPointId(SEARCH_LINE_CODE,min_distance_adjacent_point_id);
384  }
385  else {continue;}
386 
387  // TODO: For more performance skip this
388  // Check if direction of points is in range
389  int adjacent_point_direction = GetAdjacentPointDirection(SEARCH_LINE_CODE,min_distance_adjacent_point_id);
390  int origin_point_direction = table[i].GetDirection();
391 
392  int direction_difference = abs(adjacent_point_direction - origin_point_direction);
393 
394  if(direction_difference < kMaxDirectionDifference_ || (360 - kMaxDirectionDifference_) < direction_difference)

416 void LineValidationTableCreation::ExtractDirectionsInRange(vector<LineValidationTable>& line_validation_table, vector<LineValidationTable>& line_direction_in_range )
417 {
418 
419  // only take line points which have low change in direction
420  // if they have then theres an issue like a cross section
421 
422  if(line_validation_table.size()>0)
423  {
424  int cut_off_id = 0;
425  bool cut_off = false;
426 
427  int tmp_direction = line_validation_table[0].GetDirection();
428 
429  if(tmp_direction > kMinStartDirectionOnSameLine_ && tmp_direction < kMaxStartDirectionOnSameLine_)
430  {
431  for(int i=0; i<line_validation_table.size(); i++)
432  {
433  int current_direction = line_validation_table[i].GetDirection();
434  int direction_difference = abs(current_direction - tmp_direction);
435 
436  if(direction_difference > kMaxDirectionDifferenceOnSameLine_ || (360 - kMaxDirectionDifferenceOnSameLine_) < direction_difference)
437  {
438  cut_off_id = i;
439  cut_off = true;
440  break;
441  }
442  tmp_direction = current_direction;
443  }
444 
445  if(cut_off)
446  {
447  for(int i=0; i<cut_off_id; i++) line_direction_in_range.emplace_back(line_validation_table[i]);
448  }

450  copy(line_validation_table.begin(), line_validation_table.end(), back_inserter(line_direction_in_range));

642 vector<vector<Point>> LineValidationTableCreation::GetSearchRect(Point rect_mid, float search_direction)
643 {
644 
645  float rect_length_radius = kSearchRectLength_ / 2;
646  float rect_height_radius = kSearchRectHeight_ / 2;
647 
648  int length_to_corner = sqrt(pow(rect_length_radius,2)+pow(rect_height_radius,2));
649  int corner_angle = 90 - atan(rect_height_radius/rect_length_radius) * 180/PI;
650 
651  int rect_top_right_angle = search_direction - corner_angle;
652  int rect_top_left_angle = search_direction + corner_angle;
653  int rect_bottom_left_angle = search_direction + 180 - corner_angle;
654  int rect_bottom_right_angle = search_direction + 180 + corner_angle;
655 
656  if(rect_bottom_right_angle > 359) rect_top_right_angle %= 360;
657  if(rect_top_right_angle < 0) rect_top_right_angle = 360 - abs(rect_top_right_angle);
658 
659  if(rect_top_left_angle > 359) rect_top_left_angle %= 360;
660  if(rect_top_left_angle < 0) rect_top_left_angle = 360 - abs(rect_top_left_angle);
661 
662  if(rect_bottom_left_angle > 359) rect_bottom_left_angle %= 360;
663  if(rect_bottom_left_angle < 0) rect_bottom_left_angle = 360 - abs(rect_bottom_left_angle);
664 
665  if(rect_bottom_right_angle > 359) rect_bottom_right_angle %= 360;
666  if(rect_bottom_right_angle < 0) rect_bottom_right_angle = 360 - abs(rect_bottom_right_angle);
667 
668  float rect_top_right_angle_f = rect_top_right_angle * (PI/180);
669  float rect_top_left_angle_f = rect_top_left_angle * (PI/180);
670  float rect_bottom_left_angle_f = rect_bottom_left_angle * (PI/180);
671  float rect_bottom_right_angle_f = rect_bottom_right_angle * (PI/180);
672 
673  int rect_top_left_x_offset = length_to_corner * cos(rect_top_right_angle_f);
674  int rect_top_left_y_offset = -length_to_corner * sin(rect_top_right_angle_f);
675  Point rect_top_left(rect_mid.x + rect_top_left_x_offset, rect_mid.y + rect_top_left_y_offset);
676 
677  int rect_top_right_x_offset = length_to_corner * cos(rect_top_left_angle_f);
678  int rect_top_right_y_offset = -length_to_corner * sin(rect_top_left_angle_f);
679  Point rect_top_right(rect_mid.x + rect_top_right_x_offset, rect_mid.y + rect_top_right_y_offset);
680 
681  int rect_bottom_left_x_offset = length_to_corner * cos(rect_bottom_left_angle_f);
682  int rect_bottom_left_y_offset = -length_to_corner * sin(rect_bottom_left_angle_f);
683  Point rect_bottom_left(rect_mid.x + rect_bottom_left_x_offset, rect_mid.y + rect_bottom_left_y_offset);
684 
685  int rect_bottom_right_x_offset = length_to_corner * cos(rect_bottom_right_angle_f);
686  int rect_bottom_right_y_offset = -length_to_corner * sin(rect_bottom_right_angle_f);
687  Point rect_bottom_right(rect_mid.x + rect_bottom_right_x_offset, rect_mid.y + rect_bottom_right_y_offset);
688 
689 
690 
691  vector<vector<Point>> contours(1);
692 
693  contours[0].push_back(rect_top_left);
694  contours[0].push_back(rect_top_right);
695  contours[0].push_back(rect_bottom_left);
696  contours[0].push_back(rect_bottom_right);
697 
698 
699 
700  return contours;
701 }
